Isamkelo Dikgaruru: Through the use of visions, dreams and historical rituals as a starting point, this play sees the protagonist exploring the ways that they can exist while having a physical body that is considered to be disabled. Details: The show takes place on November 13 to 16 at the Baxter Theatre Centre, 2 Main Road, Rondebosch.
